strategic acquisitions our teams around the world are f read more worldwide location we understand that every market is different and that our customers and their requirements are as diverse as the world in which we live with  offices worldwide our colleagues comprise over  nationalities we understand that every market is different and that our customers and their requirements are as diverse as the world in which we live with  offices worldwide our colleagues comprise over  nationalities giving us a diversity of thinking which we believe translates into a greater understanding of our customers and enabling us to make better and more informed decisions our office addresses can be found on the contact page our people our people are our business the company’s value derives ultimately from them it is on their expertise innovation drive and relationships that we depend for the development and growth of our business read more partnership  collaboration we work collaboratively with our customers and partners to identify and implement optimal solutions we invest in longterm partnerships and understand that the commercial context can vary over time working with us innovative solutions the core of our business is the distribution of energy the combination of our expertise and our presence in markets globally enables us to identify optimal solutions for our clients working with us  corporate brochure download download document the vitol foundation report established in  the vitol foundation focuses on enabling children living in deprivation to escape the cycle of poverty and reach their potent download document vitol foundation we first began making charitable grants in  and established the vitol foundation in  since then we have funded over  projects in  co read more home  vitol who we are who we are our companies vitol aviation valt varo vivo energy viva energy australia vpi immingham vtti ventspils nafta group cockett marine oil ovh energy our business in numbers vitol foun